<li id="cite_note-kotelnikov-6"><b><a href="#cite_ref-kotelnikov_6-0" title="">^</a></b> S. N. Molotkov, “Quantum cryptography and V. A. Kotel’nikov’s one-time key and sampling theorems,” PHYS-USP <b>49</b>, 750-761 (2006), article available to journal subscribers in&#160;English <a href="http://www.turpion.org/php/paper.phtml?journal_id=pu&amp;paper_id=6050" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.turpion.org/php/paper.phtml?journal_id=pu&amp;paper_id=6050" rel="nofollow">[1]</a> and openly in&#160;Russian <a href="http://www.ufn.ru/ru/articles/2006/7/k/" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.ufn.ru/ru/articles/2006/7/k/" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-schneierotp-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-schneierotp_7-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFSchneier">Schneier, Bruce. <a href="http://www.schneier.com/crypto-gram-0210.html#7" class="external text" title="http://www.schneier.com/crypto-gram-0210.html#7" rel="nofollow">"Arguments against one-time pad systems"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.schneier.com/crypto-gram-0210.html#7" class="external free" title="http://www.schneier.com/crypto-gram-0210.html#7" rel="nofollow">http://www.schneier.com/crypto-gram-0210.html#7</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Arguments+against+one-time+pad+systems&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Schneier&amp;rft.aufirst=Bruce&amp;rft.au=Schneier%2C+Bruce&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.schneier.com%2Fcrypto-gram-0210.html%237&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:One-time_pad"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFKlein2003">Klein, Melville (2003). <a href="http://www.nsa.gov/publications/publi00017.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.nsa.gov/publications/publi00017.pdf" rel="nofollow">"Securing Record Communications: The TSEC/KW-26"</a> (PDF). NSA<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.nsa.gov/publications/publi00017.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.nsa.gov/publications/publi00017.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.nsa.gov/publications/publi00017.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-05-12</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Securing+Record+Communications%3A+The+TSEC%2FKW-26&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Klein&amp;rft.aufirst=Melville&amp;rft.au=Klein%2C+Melville&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.pub=NSA&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nsa.gov%2Fpublications%2Fpubli00017.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:One-time_pad"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
